---
layout: department.njk
title: Human Resources
subtitle: City employee recruitment, benefits, training, and personnel policies.
description: Aberdeen Human Resources Department — city employment opportunities, benefits, and personnel services. Call (410) 272-1600 ext. 207.
deptPhone: "(410) 272-1600 ext. 207"
deptRealUrl: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/human-resources"
---

<div class="space-y-8">
  <div>
    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">The Human Resources Department manages all aspects of employment for the City of Aberdeen — from recruiting and hiring to benefits administration, employee training, and personnel policy compliance.</p>
    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Working for the City of Aberdeen offers <strong>greater job security and benefits</strong> than the private sector, along with the opportunity to make a meaningful difference in your community every day.</p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Services</h2>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      {% for service in [
        { title: "Recruitment & Hiring", desc: "Job postings, applications, and the hiring process." },
        { title: "Benefits Administration", desc: "Health insurance, retirement plans, and leave policies." },
        { title: "Employee Training", desc: "Professional development and required training programs." },
        { title: "Personnel Policies", desc: "City employee handbook and HR policies." },
        { title: "Classification & Compensation", desc: "Job classifications and salary administration." },
        { title: "Labor Relations", desc: "Union contract administration and grievance handling." }
      ] %}
      <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-navy mb-1">{{ service.title }}</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">{{ service.desc }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-navy rounded-xl p-6 text-white">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">We Are Hiring</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-4">The City of Aberdeen regularly posts open positions across all departments. A career with the City offers stability, benefits, and the chance to serve your neighbors.</p>
    <a href="{{ '/services/employment/' | url }}" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gov-blue text-white font-semibold px-5 py-2.5 rounded hover:bg-gov-blue-dark transition-colors duration-200 text-sm">View Current Openings</a>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Quick Links</h2>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
      {% for link in [
        { label: "View Job Openings", url: "/services/employment/" },
        { label: "City Benefits Overview", url: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/human-resources" },
        { label: "Employee Forms", url: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/human-resources" },
        { label: "Contact HR", url: "/contact/" }
      ] %}
      <a href="{{ link.url | url }}" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gov-blue hover:text-navy font-medium hover:underline py-1">
        <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        {{ link.label }}
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
